name: Mathi FlyAsh
overview:
Established in the year 2012, we, “Mathi Fly Ash Bricks Exports” have been able to stand as prominent supplier, distributor, manufacturer, exporter, retailer & trader of a wide range of Fly ash Brick and Blue Metal Chips.

These products are available in various specifications. Interlocking Concrete Blocks, Fly Ash Cement Bricks, Fly Ash Bricks, Blue Metal Chips 20 mm, Blue Metal Chips 12 mm, Blue Metal chips 40 mm and many more are some products of our range.

Our Infrastructure: An unmanaged and unsophisticated infrastructure can be a drawback for the process of the company, therefore, we have given utmost preference to the management of the infrastructure and its unit.

Quality Assurance: We have adhered to quality since our inception itself and have been offering the coveted customers with a wide variety of Flyash Brick and Blue Metal Chips. These products have been made from the best quality raw material and have been offered to the customers at comprehensive price range.

Client Satisfaction: Being a client oriented firm we have strictly directed all our actions towards the achievement of the satisfaction of the respective clients.

Our Strengths: At Mathi Fly Ash Bricks And Exports we believe that our strengths are : Ability to execute large and complex projects on a turnkey basis in a timely and cost-effective manner Operations in diverse and complementary projects. Cost competitiveness
